Release 0.2.(1|2) (May 7, 2011)
-------------------------------

- Full inclusion of html5-slides resources (files copied instead of symlinks)
  Thanks Christopher Lozinski who report it. 


Release 0.2 beta (May 1st, 2011)
---------------------------------

- Added code highlighting via pygments_. ``code-block`` and ``sourcecode`` 
  directives are supported
- Added ``footer`` directive support
- Many improvements in UI . See https://github.com/nqnwebs/html-slideshow/

.. _pygments: http://pygments.org

Release 0.1 (April 19, 2011)
----------------------------

- First public release

